Must be some sort of mistake.

27:08.043 --> 27:08.918
It's open.

27:14.507 --> 27:15.634
Lock the door, please.

27:21.097 --> 27:22.974
I didn't expect to see you again.

27:23.475 --> 27:27.520
Yeah, well, I guess I was caught
a little off guard by your, uh…

27:27.604 --> 27:29.731
what is it, pretending to be other people?

27:29.814 --> 27:31.316
They're scenarios.

27:32.567 --> 27:33.443
For fun.

27:33.985 --> 27:36.446
When I thought about it,
I guess it kinda was fun.

27:37.364 --> 27:39.491
Why don't you take off your shirt and tie?

27:58.385 --> 27:59.844
So, who am I this evening?

28:10.063 --> 28:10.939
You…

28:12.440 --> 28:14.776
are a handsome young Marine.

28:14.859 --> 28:18.655
Just stormed the beaches of Ormoc Bay
in the Philippines.

28:28.581 --> 28:32.669
You were thinking about your sweetheart
back home in Kansas.

28:33.503 --> 28:37.549
<i>So, maybe that's why,</i>
<i>when your unit entered an airfield,</i>

28:37.632 --> 28:40.760
you don't notice the machine gun nest
right in front of you.

28:41.136 --> 28:42.762
Cut it off, we are losing him!

28:42.846 --> 28:43.680
The leg.

28:43.763 --> 28:45.223
Saw it off!

28:45.306 --> 28:46.391
No, no, no!

28:53.982 --> 28:57.652
Forty-caliber rounds
tear through your right leg

28:57.736 --> 28:58.862
just below the knee.

29:03.158 --> 29:05.034
You don't feel anything at first…

29:06.703 --> 29:08.371
but as you fall to the ground…

29:09.372 --> 29:12.542
the pain washes over you,
and it's excruciating.

29:15.170 --> 29:16.713
It's <i>excruciating.</i>

29:17.130 --> 29:19.841
Oh.  Oh, God, it hurts.

29:27.599 --> 29:29.684
What, is it a little bigger
than you're used to?

29:36.024 --> 29:38.151
